# Proposal

## What will (likely) be the title of your project?

Let's Cook

## In just a sentence or two, summarize your project. (E.g., "A website that lets you buy and sell stocks.")

A game that lets you guess which character from Breaking Bad said a certain quote. 

## In a paragraph or more, detail your project. What will your software do? What features will it have? How will it be executed?

For the final project, I will be using Python, so the software that I am using is IDLE. To start off the game, the user will be given a quote from 
Breaking Bad that a specific character said, then prompt the user to guess who said it. This will be executed using a function that will include a 
list of quotes from five characters: Walter, Jesse, Saul Goodman, Hank, and Gus. Next, the software will either interpret the user's guess as correct 
or incorrect using for loops and while loops. If the user has an incorrect guess, the program willl either has them to try again or give up. But if 
the user has a correct guess, then the program will tell the user that the answer is correct, and also display an image of the character that said the quote.
In order to accomplish this, the program will have to have a file imported, so the photo is able to be used. Some other things that will be included in the 
project are if statements and the import random feature.

