The first step I would need to take is to find quotes from Breaking Bad from each of the five characters, some that are well known and some that are not so well known. The next thing that 
I would need to do is start writing the program that runs the game by creating lists of the quotes from each character. Some of the topics that I may need to research in order to complete 
the final project would be to find some short cuts in writing in python. I am somewhat confident that I have a suffient amount of knowledge on each of the features that I will be using to write 
the code for this game. I think the thing that I may struggle with the most in this project is being able to import a file into my program, I am hoping that with refreshing myself on importing 
files, by reading the textbook and watching previous lecture videos. Another step that I would need to take in order to complete this program is to be able to notice the mistakes that are in my code.
Sometimes when I am writing code, whether it be for the homework or for the labs, sometimes it takes me a little while to figure out what I am doing wrong in the code. If I am able to  complete all
of these steps and maybe some extra things along the way. I should be able to accomplish a sufficient amount of what I am hoping to show in the game. 
